<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>관리자 대시보드 - Refresh Beverage Mall</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Apple SD Gothic Neo", "Noto Sans KR", system-ui, sans-serif; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; margin: 0; padding: 40px; background-color: #f8fafc; color: #1e293b; }
        .admin-container { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 16px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); }
        .board-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 35px; border-bottom: 2px solid #0f172a; padding-bottom: 20px; }
        h2 { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; margin: 0; }
        .btn-home { color: #64748b; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
        .btn-home:hover { color: #0f172a; text-decoration: underline; }

        .menu-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 25px; margin-top: 20px; }
        .menu-card { background: #f8fafc; padding: 40px 30px; border-radius: 16px; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; color: #0f172a; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; transition: all 0.3s; }
        .menu-card:hover { background: #0ea5e9; color: white; transform: translateY(-5px); border-color: #0ea5e9; box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(14,165,233,0.2); }
        .menu-card h3 { margin: 0 0 12px 0; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; }
        .menu-card p { margin: 0; font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.9; line-height: 1.5; }
        footer { margin-top: 50px; text-align: center; font-size: 13px; color: #94a3b8; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="admin-container">
    <header class="board-header">
        <h2>👑 통합 관리자 통제실 (대시보드)</h2>
        <a href="/" class="btn-home">🏠 쇼핑몰 홈으로 복귀</a>
    </header>
    <main class="menu-grid">
        <a href="/admin/products" class="menu-card">
            <h3>📦 진열 상품 관리</h3>
            <p>상품 대장 관리 및<br>메인 노출 상태 제어</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/admin/orders" class="menu-card">
            <h3>🚚 배송/주문 관리</h3>
            <p>고객 실시간 결제건 확인<br>및 배송 상태 일괄 처리</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/admin/users" class="menu-card">
            <h3>👥 가입 회원 관리</h3>
            <p>쇼핑몰 유저 명부 열람<br>권한 조정 및 강제 추방</p>
        </a>
    </main>
    <footer>&copy; 2026 시스템 관리 센터. All rights reserved.</footer>
</div>
</body>
</html>